body_html:
I have also tried to compile the same example tests using tensorflow v1.5 branch and I got a different error:
gcc5_tensorflow_v1.5_abi0.log

The exact version of tensorflow used to create the above log was:
tf.GIT_VERSION, tf.VERSION = 'v1.3.0-rc1-6081-g6e08980', '1.5.0-rc0'

As before, the tensorflow v1.5 itself was compiled without any problems and the command to compile aot examples was:
cd tensorflow/compiler/aot/tests ; bazel clean ; bazel build --cxxopt="-D_GLIBCXX_USE_CXX11_ABI=0" all_tests &>gcc5_tensorflow_v1.5_abi0.log

I have also tried these tensorflow versions, but they gave pretty much the same error as in gcc5_abi0.log that I shared before:
('v1.4.1-0-g438604f', '1.4.1')
('v1.3.0-rc1-6508-g97a4c22', '1.4.0')
